   Quick Picks


We offer online, fax, mail and phone methods below.

Borrowing/recalling a book from our Library:

     * Place a Request in the BEACON LIBRARY CATALOG
     * Send an email to the LIBRARY
     * Fax your request to x4-1927
     * Mail your request to Library 111-113
     * Call the Reference Desk at x4-4200

   More on borrowing/recalling books

Buying Books:

     * Complete the online order form for a BOOK
     * Send an email to the LIBRARY
     * Fax your request to x4-1927
     * Mail your request to Library 111-113
     * Call the Reference Desk at x4-4200

   More on buying books

   IT Bookstore Information

Renew books from the JPL Library:

     * Call Library Circulation x4-3840

